  <div class="card">
    <div class="body">
      <span>
        <strong style="font-size:16px;">Step 1: Download CSV Template</strong>
      </span>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 mt-4">
          <p>Download the template and fill in the data without changing the format. Re-Upload the file in the below form. ( The system will add new data parsing each row. So make sure you add no duplicates )</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 text-left">
          <%= link_to '/template.csv', target: 'blank', class: "btn btn-sm btn-primary" do %>
            <i class="fa fa-download"></i> Download
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <%= render partial: 'admin/upload_translations/form/form' %>
  </div>